{"tid":2062867,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約州長簽令警務改革禁鎖喉 列為C級重罪，最高入獄15年","createTime":"2020-06-13T12:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T15:43:49.000Z","uid":113000,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e877adc771ab15676db35edfcaea19f22afe3fcb","tid":2062867,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"紐約州長科莫（Andrew Cuomo）周五（12日）簽署一系列警務改革，當中包括將鎖喉等有爭議的拘捕手法列為非法，以及一系列旨在加強警員問責的改革。他表示將簽署行政命令，將警隊改革跟州政府撥款掛勾，規定州政府撥款只會給予有立法規管警隊改革根絕種族主義的市政府。他稱，警察部門就根除系統性種族歧視改造及現代化，才能符合獲得州政府撥款的資格。<br />\n<br />\n科莫簽署的改革引起警察工會不滿，認為新法反警方，對警方不公。紐約警察已禁止鎖喉，但<span style=\"color: red;\">新法將鎖喉或其他類似制服手段列為C級重罪，最高入獄15年。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20200613/s00005/1592023408584/%E7%B4%90%E7%B4%84%E5%B7%9E%E9%95%B7%E7%B0%BD%E4%BB%A4%E8%AD%A6%E5%8B%99%E6%94%B9%E9%9D%A9%E7%A6%81%E9%8E%96%E5%96%89-%E8%AD%A6%E5%AF%9F%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8D%E6%BB%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200613%2Fs00005%2F1592023408584%2F%25E7%25B4%2590%25E7%25B4%2584%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E5%2596%2589-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF&d=9%2FF7mzj%2FI7OrL%2BCOzrVJrkBSGL744lGwoqCHTcH8MN0%3D&h=00f7dbfe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20200613%2Fs00005%2F1592023408584%2F%25E7%25B4%2590%25E7%25B4%2584%25E5%25B7%259E%25E9%2595%25B7%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E4%25BB%25A4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258B%2599%25E6%2594%25B9%25E9%259D%25A9%25E7%25A6%2581%25E9%258E%2596%25E5%2596%2589-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%25AF%259F%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E6%259C%2583%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%25BB%25BF&h=655a698c\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9